query:
INSERT INTO island_guides (name, slug, atoll, overview, topThingsToDo, flightInfo, speedboatInfo, ferryInfo, bestTimeToVisit, published) VALUES
('Male - The Capital City', 'male-capital-city', 'North Malé Atoll', 'The vibrant capital of Maldives, Male is a bustling city with colorful buildings, rich history, and local culture. Home to the iconic Friday Mosque and National Centre, Male offers a unique glimpse into Maldivian urban life.', 'Friday Mosque,National Centre,Male City Centre,Local Markets,Artificial Beach', 'Fly into Velana International Airport (main international airport)', '20 minutes by speedboat from airport to Male city', '30 minutes by ferry from airport to Male city', 'November to April', 1),
('Maafushi Island', 'maafushi-island', 'South Malé Atoll', 'A popular local island known for its vibrant community, beautiful beaches, and water sports. Maafushi offers authentic Maldivian experiences with local guesthouses, restaurants serving fresh seafood, and easy access to snorkeling and diving sites.', 'Snorkeling,Diving,Local Markets,Beach Volleyball,Fishing', 'No direct flights - use Male airport as gateway', '45 minutes speedboat from Male airport', '1.5 hours public ferry from Male city', 'November to April', 1),
('Thulusdhoo Island', 'thulusdhoo-island', 'North Malé Atoll', 'Known as the surfing capital of Maldives, Thulusdhoo attracts surfers from around the world. The island features consistent waves, a laid-back atmosphere, and excellent local restaurants. Perfect for water sports enthusiasts and beach lovers.', 'Surfing,Snorkeling,Diving,Local Restaurants,Beach Bars', 'No direct flights - use Male airport', '40 minutes speedboat from Male airport', '1.5 hours public ferry from Male city', 'March to October', 1),
('Banana Reef', 'banana-reef', 'North Malé Atoll', 'A world-renowned diving and snorkeling destination famous for its abundant marine life and coral formations. Banana Reef is an atoll perfect for underwater exploration with pristine coral gardens and schools of tropical fish.', 'Diving,Snorkeling,Coral Gardens,Tropical Fish,Manta Rays', 'No direct flights - use Male airport', '30 minutes speedboat from Male or nearby resorts', 'Day trips available from Male', 'November to April', 1),
('Dhigurah Island', 'dhigurah-island', 'Ari Atoll', 'A picturesque island in Ari Atoll known for its pristine beaches, vibrant coral reefs, and whale shark encounters. Dhigurah is perfect for families and offers a perfect blend of relaxation and adventure.', 'Whale Shark Watching,Snorkeling,Diving,Beach Relaxation,Island Hopping', '45 minutes domestic flight from Male to Ari Atoll', '30 minutes speedboat from Ari Atoll to Dhigurah', '2.5 hours speedboat from Male to Dhigurah', 'June to November', 1),
('Ukulhas Island', 'ukulhas-island', 'Ari Atoll', 'A charming local island with authentic Maldivian culture, beautiful beaches, and excellent diving opportunities. Ukulhas offers a genuine island experience away from resort crowds with local guesthouses and restaurants.', 'Diving,Snorkeling,Local Culture,Beach Walks,Fishing', '45 minutes domestic flight from Male to Ari Atoll', '20 minutes speedboat from Ari Atoll to Ukulhas', '2 hours speedboat from Male to Ari Atoll', 'November to April', 1),
('Veligandu Island', 'veligandu-island', 'Ari Atoll', 'Famous for its stunning lagoon and pristine white sand beaches, Veligandu is an ideal destination for relaxation and water activities. The island is known for its excellent snorkeling right from the beach.', 'Snorkeling,Beach Relaxation,Diving,Water Sports,Sunset Watching', '45 minutes domestic flight from Male to Ari Atoll', '25 minutes speedboat from Ari Atoll to Veligandu', '2.5 hours speedboat from Male to Veligandu', 'November to April', 1),
('Kandooma Island', 'kandooma-island', 'South Malé Atoll', 'A scenic island in South Malé Atoll known for its excellent diving sites, vibrant coral reefs, and diverse marine life. Kandooma offers both relaxation and adventure for all types of travelers.', 'Diving,Snorkeling,Coral Reefs,Tropical Fish,Beach Relaxation', 'No direct flights - use Male airport', '30 minutes speedboat from Male airport', '1.5 hours public ferry from Male city', 'November to April', 1),
('Fulidhoo Island', 'fulidhoo-island', 'Vaavu Atoll', 'A traditional fishing village island offering authentic Maldivian experiences. Fulidhoo is known for its friendly locals, fresh seafood, and unspoiled beaches away from tourist crowds.', 'Local Culture,Fishing Village,Beach Exploration,Local Cuisine,Photography', '40 minutes domestic flight from Male to Vaavu', '20 minutes speedboat from Vaavu to Fulidhoo', '1.5 hours speedboat from Male to Vaavu Atoll', 'November to April', 1),
('Haa Alifu Atoll', 'haa-alifu-atoll', 'Haa Alifu Atoll', 'The northernmost atoll of Maldives, Haa Alifu offers pristine beaches, excellent diving, and authentic island culture. Less crowded than southern atolls, it is perfect for travelers seeking solitude and natural beauty.', 'Diving,Snorkeling,Pristine Beaches,Local Culture,Fishing', '1 hour domestic flight from Male to Haa Alifu', '30 minutes speedboat from Haa Alifu airport', '3-4 hours speedboat from Male to Haa Alifu', 'November to April', 1)
